    <div class="container body-content">
        <div class="dualcolumns-container">
            <div class="page-header">
                <h2>
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-check " aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    用户登录
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-5">
                    <div class="container" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
                        <div class="row">
                            <a class="visible-sm visible-xs pull-right" show-introduction="">
                                <span class="fa fa-question-circle"></span><span style="margin-left:4px;">
                                    说明
                                </span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <form>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>用户名：（* 必填）</label>
                            <input class="form-control input-validation-error" data-val="true" data-val-length="* 用户名的长度不能大于20" data-val-length-max="20" data-val-remote="* 用户名不存在" data-val-remote-additionalfields="*.UserName" data-val-remote-url="/User/_NameNotExist" data-val-required="* 用户名不能为空" id="UserName" name="UserName" placeholder="不是昵称，是登录用户名" type="text" value="" aria-required="true" aria-describedby="UserName-error">
                            <span class="field-validation-error" data-valmsg-for="UserName" data-valmsg-replace="true"><span id="UserName-error" class="">* 用户名不能为空</span></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>密码：（* 必填）</label>
                            <input class="form-control input-validation-error" data-val="true" data-val-length="* 密码的长度不能小于4，大于20" data-val-length-max="20" data-val-length-min="4" data-val-required="* 密码不能为空" id="Password" name="Password" placeholder="不少于4个字符" type="password" aria-required="true" aria-describedby="Password-error" aria-invalid="true">
                            <span class="field-validation-error" data-valmsg-for="Password" data-valmsg-replace="true"><span id="Password-error" class="">* 密码的长度不能小于4，大于20</span></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>验证码：（* 必填）</label>
                            <br>
                            <span zyf-img-code="">

                                <input class="form-control input-validation-error" data-val="true" data-val-length="* 验证码的长度只能等于4" data-val-length-max="4" data-val-length-min="4" data-val-required="* 验证码不能为空" id="InputImageCode" name="InputImageCode" style="width:80px; display: inline;" type="text" value="" aria-required="true" aria-describedby="InputImageCode-error">

                                <a name="imageCode">

                                </a><a href="#" zyf-refresh-image-code="" style="font-size: 12px;">
                                    看不清楚
                                </a>
                                <span zyf-image-code-reminder="" style="display: none;">点击输入框显示</span>
                                <span zyf-image-code-error="" class="field-validation-error"></span>
                                <br>
                                <span class="field-validation-error" data-valmsg-for="InputImageCode" data-valmsg-replace="true"><span id="InputImageCode-error" class="">* 验证码不能为空</span></span>
                            </span>


                        </div>
                        <div class="submit">
                            <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary loading" value="提交" zyf-submit-once="" style="display: inline-block;" submit="true">

                            <label class="checkbox-inline" style="margin-left:16px;">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="remember" value="true" checked="">记住我
                            </label>
                            <span class="pull-right btn">
                                <a href="/Password/Forget">(｡ŏ_ŏ) 忘了</a>
                                <a href="/Register/Home?prepage=%2fProblem%3fexcludeCanceled%3dtrue%26excludeRewarded%3dtrue" style="margin-left:10px;"><span class="fa fa-registered"></span> 注册</a>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </form>


                    <div class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="introductionLabel">
                        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
                            <div class="modal-content">
                                <div class="modal-header">
                                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">×</span></button>
                                    <h4 class="modal-title" id="introductionLabel"></h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="modal-body">
                                </div>
                                <div class="modal-footer">
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">知道了</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 visible-lg visible-md">
                    <div page-introduction="">
                        <h3 class="text-info" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign "></span> 说明</h3>
                        <ol class="page-introduction-ol" zyf-page-introduction-body="">

                            <li>我们希望通过<a href="/About/Us">一起帮</a>，能<span class="text-primary text-bold">直接解决</span>大家在<span class="text-primary">电脑操作/软件使用/编程学习</span>等方面的<span class="text-primary text-bold">具体问题</span>。</li>
                            <li>现在互联网远程技术<span class="text-muted">（比如QQ桌面共享）</span>已经非常成熟，当我们再遇到上述问题，如果别人能<span class="text-primary">直接远程给予帮助</span>，岂不是好？</li>
                            <li>当然，你也可以在你熟悉的领域去<span class="text-primary">帮助别人</span>。由此而形成我们这个“你帮他他帮我我帮你，大家一起帮”的网上互助社区平台。</li>
                            <li>公平起见，我们还引入了 帮帮<span class="water">点</span>/<span class="credit">币</span>/<span class="bean">豆</span> 三级概念，以记录和衡量社区成员的收获和贡献。</li>
                            <li>赶快加入我们，赚取帮帮币吧！</li>

                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
